name: Multi Layer Stencil Medium Canvas
description: A multi layer stencil portrait. Aerosol paints on a 50cm x 50cm deep edge canvas. This piece of artwork is an example. It consists of several layers of aerosol paint being applied using unique hand cut stencils. Click on the 'Add to Cart' button below to order your own urban portrait in this style. You will then have the opportunity to supply a selection of your own photos for me to work from and choose what colours you would prefer to be used. Click here for more details. The photo in the corner of the portrait is there to highlight the likeness that can be achieved through urban portraits.
